items.title: MLB: Tigers didn't intentionally hit umpire
items.summary: Major League Baseball is reviewing the circumstances surrounding the pitch from Tigers right-hander Buck Farmer that hit home-plate umpire Quinn Wolcott in the shoulder after catcher James McCann and manager Brad Ausmus were ejected from Wednesday's 5-3 loss to the Indians.
items.content: Major League Baseball is reviewing the circumstances surrounding the pitch from Tigers right-hander Buck Farmer that hit home-plate umpire Quinn Wolcott in the shoulder after catcher James McCann and manager Brad Ausmus were ejected from Wednesday's 5-3 loss to the Indians.
